<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad Wiemer, Diener der Stadt</head><p>Der Rat übersendet seinen Verzeihbrief und weist zur Überreichung an Herzog Ludwig VII. von Bayern-Ingolstadt an, wenn der Jude Lesar N. freigelassen wird und seine Habe zurückerhält.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_371" id="184v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_371_r1l1"><expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> wymer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dyener </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_371_r1l2"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>euntſchaft</ex></expan> beuor Lieber . VVymer . Als Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l3"> <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / 
<del rend="strikethrough">von des Juden leſar Juden <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l4">
<del rend="strikethrough"> bey vns geſeſſen . Als der gefangen iſt </del> / VVie 
<del rend="strikethrough">den </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l5">vnſer <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> hercʒog ludwig geſchaft vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l6">hab / den 
<del rend="strikethrough">dy dabey gevveſen ſein / . <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> Juden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l7">ledig cʒulaſſen vnd Jm das ſein gencʒlich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l8"><expan>widercʒegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd cʒekeren etc Vnd alſo ſenden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l10">vvir euch darauff <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒeihbrief</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_371_line_1577280438906_3834">nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat form </ab></add> hyrynne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l11"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> . vnd wenn der Jude Alſo ledig vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_371_line_1595481155678_154">Jm </ab></add> das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l12">ſein wider oder aber gekert wirdet / So gebt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l13"><expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒeihbrief</expan> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dar / vnd ſüſt niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_371_r1l14"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> v </del> ij̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthoni </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_371" id="184v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Wymer, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        dyener</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>euntschaft</ex></expan> bevor. Lieber Wymer, als ir uns
                                <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie unser
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> herczog Ludwig geschaft und
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hab, den juden ledig
                        czu lassen und im das sein genczlich <expan>widerczegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und cze keren etc., und also senden wir euch darauff
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>czeihbrief</expan>
<add>nach <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat form </add> hyrynne
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan>; und wenn der jude also ledig und
                            <add>im</add> das sein wider oder aber gekert wirdet, so gebt
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>czeihbrief</expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dar und süst niht.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthoni.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
